en=>'When the application reaches the ICS/SOX Focus, this is documented in the application. By default, the application default is automatically transferred to this field. If this field is set to "Yes", a quality rule is used to check whether system operation is SOX-compliant. This is confirmed by the provider, for example, using the field SAS70= Yes.'
